44:58.417 --> 45:00.542
- Go, Michael!

45:01.876 --> 45:03.876
Go! Run!

45:03.918 --> 45:06.751
- (Struggling grunt)

45:03.918 --> 45:06.751
(Slicing blow)

45:06.792 --> 45:08.667
