Soldier: Lock the gates quickly!

45:10.209 --> 45:11.626
(Muskets clank)

45:11.667 --> 45:12.751
(Musket clatters)

45:12.792 --> 45:14.083
- Please, Declan!

45:14.125 --> 45:16.667
- By order of Lord Benton,

45:14.125 --> 45:16.667
Governor of Fort James,

